      "relations": null,
      "text": [
        " سَأَلْتُهُ عَنْ أُمِّ الْوَلَدِ تُبَاعُ فِي الدَّيْنِ قَالَ نَعَمْ فِي ثَمَنِ رَقَبَتِهَا ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Al Husayn Bin Muhammad, from Moala Bin Muhammad, from Al Hassan Bin Ali, from Hammad Bin Usman, from Umar Bin Yazeed, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Al-Hassan<sup>asws</sup>, said, ‘I asked him<sup>asws</sup> about a mother of the child, (can) she be sold regarding the debt. He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘Yes, regarding a price of her slavery’."
        ]
      }
